<reference id="colspec" xml:lang="en-us">
   <title>
      <keyword>colspec</keyword>
   </title>
   <shortdesc>The &lt;<keyword>colspec</keyword>&gt; element contains a column specification
for a table, including assigning a column name and number, cell content alignment,
and column width.</shortdesc>
   <prolog>
